  .section
    .row
      .column.large-7.hide-for-large-up
        .icon.h2.background-contain(style="background-image: url('/images/faces-cell-complete.png'); height:15em;")
      .column.large-5
        h2.header__bottom-border__large-left.padding-top Secure, Shared Wallets
        h5.margin-bottom Pockets is a true token wallet, not an account service. Secure your personal funds with multiple signatures, or just one.
        p Take security into your own hands and avoid trusting third parties with your savings. Like a joint-checking account, your Pockets wallet can have multiple users. To send money or tokens, the group approves each transaction.
        p Manage shared funds with friends and coworkers. Share a wallet with your child and introduce them to tokens. Token Pockets makes sharing a wallet simple and secure.
      .column.large-7.show-for-large-up
        .icon.h2.background-contain

          //- Animation starts
          img.side-phone.fade-in-right.wow.animated(src="/images/faces-cell.png" s18n-attrs="src") 
          img.user-face.user-face-position1.delay-1.fade-in-right.wow.animated(src="/images/user1.svg") 
          img.user-face.user-face-position2.delay-1.fade-in-right.wow.animated(src="/images/user2.svg") 
          img.user-face.user-face-position3.delay-1.fade-in-right.wow.animated(src="/images/user3.svg") 
          img.user-checked.check-position1.delay-4.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/user-checked.svg") 
          img.user-checked.check-position2.delay-8.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/user-checked.svg") 
          img.user-checked.check-position3.delay-12.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/user-checked.svg") 
          img.user-checked-phone.check-phone-position1.delay-6.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/user-checked-phone.svg")
          img.user-checked-phone.check-phone-position2.delay-10.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/user-checked-phone.svg")
          img.user-checked-phone.check-phone-position3.delay-14.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/user-checked-phone.svg")
          img.phone-green-screen.delay-16.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/side-phone-screen2.png" s18n-attrs="src" )
          //- Animation ends
     
     
  .section.bg-gray
    .row
      .column.large-7.hide-for-large-up
      .column.large-7.show-for-large-up
          //- Animation starts
          img.base-phone.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/inventory-screen2.png" s18n-attrs="src") 
      .column.large-5
        h2.header__bottom-border__large-left.padding-top Inventory Management
        h5.margin-bottom-less Token Pockets makes it simple to keep your #[em tokenized] perks organized.
        p Tokens can be used for media access, digital licensing, as collectable badges, represent video game assets and much more. Pockets makes it easy to manage tokens, and tokens make digital experiences more seamless, intuitive and engaging.
        p Store the tokens you acquire in your Token Pockets wallet "token inventory". You are able to freely send, receive and trade your tokens. More tokens means more perks you can enjoy!
        p Click on your token to see how many are in the global supply and learn about its details.
     
     
        
  .section.bg-gray.multi-wallets
    .row
      .column.large-7.hide-for-large-up
        .icon.h2.background-contain(style="background-image: url('/images/multiple-wallets.png'); height:15em;")
      .column.large-7.show-for-large-up
