          img.purple-wallet.delay-6.fade-in-up.wow.animated(src="/images/purple-wallet.png" s18n-attrs="src") 
          //- Animation ends
      .column.large-5
        h2.header__bottom-border__large-left.padding-top Multiple Wallets,#[br] One App
        h5.margin-bottom-less No more tedious address management.
        p The Token Pockets app securely stores multiple, distinct, token-enabled bitcoin wallets, allowing both business and privacy-conscious users to keep funds and tokens carefully separated.
        p Manage personal, business, and testnet wallets easily, all without leaving the app. Pockets uses hierarchical-deterministic (HD) wallets, allowing for secure in-app wallet generation and backup.


  .section.bg-tokenly-dark
