          img.base-phone.fade-in.wow.animated(src="/images/connecting_to_tokenpass.png" s18n-attrs="src") 
      .column.large-5
        h2.header__bottom-border__large-left.padding-top Connecting to Tokenpass
        h5.margin-bottom-less Connect your wallet to your Tokenpass account for access to perks on participating platforms.
        p In order for you to ride the token super highway, you will need to hook up one of your pockets to your browser using your Tokenpass account.
        p Once connected, when you are logged in with Tokenpass you will be able to enjoy any perks that tokens in your inventory offer.
        p To find out what your tokens do, just click on them.
        a(href="https://tokenpass.tokenly.com" target="_blank").uppercase.bold.white.btn.btn-blue-solid.btn-margin.margin-top Sign up on Tokenpass
     


  .section
    .row
      .column.large-7.hide-for-large-up
        .icon.h2.background-contain(style="background-image: url('/images/code-trust.png'); height:15em;" s18n-attrs="style") 
