        p Dozens of bitcoin developers have already contributed to Copay, and we're not finished yet. Every part of Copay, wallet and server, is available to be reviewed, improved, and developed by the community.
        p You can follow along, discuss improvements, and join in on GitHub at #[a(href="https://github.com/tokenly/pockets") tokenly/pockets], #[a(href="https://github.com/bitpay/copay") bitpay/copay] and #[a(href="https://github.com/bitpay/bitcore-wallet-service") bitpay/bitcore-wallet-service].
